query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(c cr dd hd cc) NoNestLoop(c cc cr dd hd ca) */ select cc.cc_call_center_id AS call_center,
cc.cc_name AS call_center_name,
cc.cc_manager AS manager,
sum(cr.cr_net_loss) AS returns_loss
from date_dim AS dd
inner join catalog_returns AS cr
on cr.cr_returned_date_sk = dd.d_date_sk AND dd.d_year = 2001 AND dd.d_moy = 12
inner join customer AS c
on cr.cr_returning_customer_sk = c.c_customer_sk
inner join household_demographics AS hd
on hd.hd_demo_sk = c.c_current_hdemo_sk AND hd.hd_buy_potential like 'Unknown%'
inner join call_center AS cc
on cr.cr_call_center_sk = cc.cc_call_center_sk
inner join customer_address AS ca
on ca.ca_address_sk = c.c_current_addr_sk AND ca.ca_gmt_offset = -7
inner join customer_demographics AS cd
on cd.cd_demo_sk = c.c_current_cdemo_sk AND ( ( cd.cd_marital_status = 'M' AND cd.cd_education_status = 'Unknown') OR ( cd.cd_marital_status = 'W' AND cd.cd_education_status = 'Advanced Degree')) group by cc.cc_call_center_id, cc.cc_name, cc.cc_manager, cd.cd_marital_status, cd.cd_education_status order by sum(cr.cr_net_loss) desc;
